  "plot_summary": "[HANG0] Marvel's constant barrage of people offering to buy and sell back issues comes to a head in the letters page of [LINK:1963:FF_15|FF #15], where they finally say they can't print such letters anymore and to instead contact the \"mag called the COMICOLLECTOR, published by Ronn Foss\" (and provides his address).&nbsp; Anyone wishing to buy, sell or trade are encouraged to contact him.&nbsp; Interestingly enough, today you can find back issues of COMICOLLECTOR on sale at auctions.&nbsp; It's considered one of the earliest fanzines.&nbsp; Ronn apparently died in the year 2001.",
